snippet.title: 64th Street Arcade on PS4. Full Walkthrough. Arcade Archives
snippet.description:
Gumshoe detective vs one armed, one legged pirate in downtown Chicago 🤔 Seems legit! This is a full walkthrough featuring multiple enemies and pirates but it's not  part of the Marvel multiverse (thang god!)

Original Japanese language version available on PS4 via the psn store. It seems like Arcade Archives have gotten too lazy with their ports to source the English language versions. I'm fuming. I'm honestly fuming 😁 Now if you just port Vendetta and Wrestlefest arcades all will be forgiven.
